Name
       zoomOut - Zooms out from the viewable window by two times

Syntax
       zoomOut [-help]

       Zooms out from the viewable window by two times.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description of the zoomOut command.

              For  a detailed description of the command, use the man command:
              man zoomOut.

